title: 40 Danielle LaPorte: Desire Creates Everything
description: Finally, another goddess on the School of Greatness. She's an author, speaker, entrepreneur and blogger who mixes self development with spirituality in a way that shines with purpose and passion. It's an honor to have the creator of the Desire Map, Danielle LaPorte.
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
